Set the initial value
of the matrix A.

00:04:13.110 --> 00:04:16.720
Here is the critical point.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:20.950
Here is an initial value
near the critical point.

00:04:20.950 --> 00:04:24.210
Integrate from 0 to 30.

