I want to write a program
called Lorenz GUI.

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:02.340
Lorenz Graphic User Interface.

00:06:02.340 --> 00:06:08.190
That's out of my old book
calle this one is really

00:06:08.190 --> 00:06:11.750
